		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You could see if the hack works on the PAL version of Castlevania, or try to hack the game to support the sprite split on PAL. I noticed the Sprite Split on the NTSC version strangely doesn't work on PAL systems but the PAL version's split works on both NTSC and PAL, atleast through a brief test using FCEUX.

		

		</td>
